To install on lighthouse, scp and ssh into box and use command:
  sudo ./install.lighthouse.sh
You will need to manually edit the librarian.ini file to include "ssid = yes" under the [plugins] section and "ssid" under the [dashboard] section.
Wait for librarian to restart and the plugin should be ready for use.

To install on pi, scp and ssh into the pi and use command:
  sudo ./install.pi.sh
You will need to manually edit the two librarian.ini files to include "ssid = yes" under the [plugins] section and "ssid" under the [dashboard] section.
Wait for librarian to restart and the plugin should be ready for use.

Please note that you must connect to the new SSID when the connection has been lost.
